profile_summary: I'm a dedicated AI and ML enthusiast, currently pursuing an Integrated MSc in Computer Science with a specialization in AI and Data Science, proficient in C++, TypeScript, and R, with a strong presence on GitHub through my 26 public repositories. As a detail-oriented developer, I leverage my technical skills to drive innovation and improve everyday life, and I'm excited to collaborate and share my knowledge with like-minded professionals. With a growing network of peers and a passion for continuous learning, I'm committed to delivering high-quality solutions that make a lasting impact.
